    <img src="https://images.code.org/1ea42f431145cd7c5cb4285f410bbead-image-1744322831445.07.07 PM.png" alt="A level progression for the sequences explore lesson, showing the check-in and assessment levels" style="width: 30%; border-radius: 5px;">

